r with efforts in the far infrared, this work\nopens a window to the elementary quantum dynamics of light and matter in an\nenergy range at the boundary between vacuum and thermal background conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2016 13:09:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-15"}
